hokku-server (2.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Web GUI with config editor, image grid, screen tracking
  * Multi-screen support with X-Screen-Name header
  * Server-driven sleep schedule (X-Sleep-Seconds header)
  * Fair image distribution with show_index ranking
  * Configurable orientation (landscape/portrait)
  * EXIF orientation support
  * Debian packaging with systemd service

